      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2705-2741",
      "markText": "吾宁忍过去国粹之消亡，而不忍现在及将来之民族，不适世界之生存而归消灭也。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300057902&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2705&rangeEnd=2741",
